00:55:26,256 --> 00:55:34,106
Look at his glasses.
Look at his hair--does it need pomade?

521
00:55:36,266 --> 00:55:39,986
We have checked
the make-up carefully.

522
00:55:40,604 --> 00:55:45,993
As for acting, there are interior
and exterior aspects.

523
00:55:46,844 --> 00:55:53,324
The actors use body language
to express themselves.

524
00:55:55,986 --> 00:56:04,806
Every expression of the eye,
from the stern look to the weak gaze--

525
00:56:06,129 --> 00:56:10,229
we consider every detail.

