545
00:57:50,600 --> 00:57:55,900
And I said, "Uncle Chi, how about
playing the harmonica now?"

546
00:57:56,707 --> 00:58:00,987
Actually, this is very interesting.

547
00:58:01,678 --> 00:58:04,607
This is a kind of atmosphere,
and [ want to say just now

