00:58:05,115 --> 00:58:08,075
how to create
an atmosphere for a character.

549
00:58:08,585 --> 00:58:13,805
He won't come to you and say,
"l will play the harmonica after the killing.

550
00:58:14,624 --> 00:58:16,584
I will play ‘Friends Forever."

