00:58:16,960 --> 00:58:19,240
won't say it out, but he will do it,

552
00:58:19,629 --> 00:58:21,799
and it creates an atmosphere
at the scene.

553
00:58:22,232 --> 00:58:27,832
This is a kind of soft promotion
of atmosphere, which is very interesting,

554
00:58:28,705 --> 00:58:35,125
with the playing of
"Friends Forever" at his own pace.

555
00:58:36,079 --> 00:58:39,709
In the end we filmed two versions,
one with "Friends Forever"

556
00:58:40,484 --> 00:58:42,944
and the other without.

