629
01:05:36,166 --> 01:05:40,086
He acts on the gang leader's orders.

630
01:05:40,703 --> 01:05:43,803
If the leader tells him to hit
his head against the wall, he will hit it.

631
01:05:44,507 --> 01:05:47,347
If he is told to smash his head,
