638
01:06:08,965 --> 01:06:10,305
He doesn't need to think.

639
01:06:13,503 --> 01:06:17,723
The scene where
he and I go to Thailand,

640
01:06:18,575 --> 01:06:22,915
he only says he wants a threesome,
a massage, and some shark's fin soup.

641
01:06:23,613 --> 01:06:26,363
He is so simple.

642
01:06:26,850 --> 01:06:30,250
When there is an accident,
he takes a potshot with two guns.

643
01:06:30,820 --> 01:06:34,720
And he says, "Brother,
you go and I'll handle it.”

644
01:06:35,558 --> 01:06:37,868
He doesn't think of
whether he can actually handle it.

