01:06:38,294 --> 01:06:41,723
I think, on some level,
in the gangster movies,

646
01:06:42,298 --> 01:06:44,758
there are some people
who just give suggestions

647
01:06:45,168 --> 01:06:47,568
and are always
planning things for you.

648
01:06:48,004 --> 01:06:49,874
These people
will always remain in the background.

649
01:06:50,206 --> 01:06:52,486
In the front,
there will always be a person

650
01:06:52,909 --> 01:06:54,839
who blocks the bullet
for you with his body,

651
01:06:55,211 --> 01:06:56,471
as if he is your shield.

652
01:06:57,847 --> 01:06:59,577
