01:10:15,778 --> 01:10:17,448
that kind of passion,

678
01:10:17,747 --> 01:10:21,997
that feeling when you are so helpless
and cannot turn to anyone.

679
01:10:22,685 --> 01:10:25,265
And the feelings between brothers--

680
01:10:25,722 --> 01:10:29,062
one minute you had your brother,
