I may better understand my performance.

805
01:25:13,642 --> 01:25:15,812
When you're first starting out,

806
01:25:16,178 --> 01:25:19,778
you should watch your films
and improve yourself.

807
01:25:20,549 --> 01:25:22,449
Even if it has become fact,

808
01:25:22,818 --> 01:25:27,328
you should try looking it
from a mature perspective.

809
01:25:28,056 --> 01:25:34,266
